Package edu.ncsu.csc216.stp.model.test_plans

Class AbstractTestPlan

java.lang.Object
edu.ncsu.csc216.stp.model.test_plans.AbstractTestPlan
Direct Known Subclasses:
FailingTestList, TestPlan
public abstract class AbstractTestPlan extends Object
Abstract class for different kinds of TestPlans. Main functionality is in managing it's list of TestCases, as well as providing access to the TestCase's methods. Maintains a name for comparison to other classes that extend this one.
Author:
Jeremiah Knizley, Ryan McPhee
